custom.Description: Logical And node. Runs all children until it reaches a FAILURE (can allow multiple failures if desired.)
Selector nodes have one or more children and run through them until meeting some condition or completing them all

custom.SQL: SELECT ProgressionTreeType as PageGroupID, Name, 20 as SortIndex FROM ProgressionTrees WHERE ProgressionTreeType in (SELECT UniqueCultureProgressionTree from Civilizations)
SELECT Description as Text from Ages where AgeType=?1
SELECT CivilizationType as PageID, null as PageGroupID, 'Gameplay' as PageLayoutID, Name, 10 as SortIndex FROM Civilizations where StartingCivilizationLevelType = 'CIVILIZATION_LEVEL_FULL_CIV'
